{"tid":698276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山寨獅身人面像「借屍還魂」　埃及震怒","createTime":"2018-06-11T14:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T05:15:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4cff172ff9877efc5cda302f38bd7c1c9ecf6ca2","tid":698276,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:11:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180611/20416713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20416713&d=d47Jhd%2F5q78A9mdh97v8s1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=0bc767b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F20416713&h=139970d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180611/20416713</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月11日 <br />\n<br />\n山寨獅身人面像「借屍還魂」　埃及震怒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180611/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180611%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=47e78698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■山寨獅身人面像被拍到身首重新組裝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地山寨技術堪稱登峯造極。河北石家莊一個聲稱是1比1仿製的獅身人面像，兩年前因埃及向聯合國教科文組織投訴而被拆除，身首分離。未料近日再傳山寨獅身人面像「復活」，並準備重新組裝，事件再觸怒埃及，埃及文物部斥「極其無禮」，已向聯合國和中方交涉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180611/large/a1303b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180611%2Flarge%2Fa1303b.gif&h=c968817b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■獅身人面像內設有「皇宮」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年辯稱拍戲場景<br />\n<br />\n座落河北長城文創園的山寨獅身人面像，身長約60米，高約20米，2014年以1比1仿造而成，其中獅身有門，裏面是兩層高的宮殿。埃及古物部部長曾批評，山寨版細節處理粗糙，褻瀆埃及文化遺產。園區當年辯稱，是拍戲用的臨時性場景，拍攝完畢就拆除改景，2016年拆除後身首分離。<br />\n<br />\n《河北青年報》近日披露，該獅身人面像身將再度合體，現場有工人施工及進行改造工程。事件再引埃及不滿，埃及文物部表示，準備重新向聯合國教科文組織投訴，和中國外交部要求拆除山寨貨，又批評事件是對埃及文明遺產極其無禮。除石家莊外，安徽滁州長城夢世界旅遊文創園、蘭州新區長城夢世界旅遊文創園，各有一座山寨獅身人面像。<br />\n<br />\n觀察者網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n日開車12小時　月薪僅7,400元　<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n學霸失第一13刀殺同學　專家：或是香港問題放大版"},{"pid":"ef2f492f3a01e771852dda544073290c1b892fc0","tid":698276,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"月亮同火星D金字塔係咪中國人過去起"},{"pid":"a36ff3b45bde53a507a68bf559f8d2331757e359","tid":698276,"uid":42188,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:14:26.000Z","msg":"埃及人未富先驕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760d330123d31b3bb0ceebb823e6c16fb3b8326a","tid":698276,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:15:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1621b416fa2100f38a9c07f3a53bd60ba283a463","tid":698276,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:19:32.000Z","msg":"中國人複製同做假真係世界第一"},{"pid":"5cf93027e9a8897139149accc256b4da41bea106","tid":698276,"uid":51436,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:23:03.000Z","msg":"獅身人面像是世界的，小印度憑什麼對我們贏國的內政說三道四？"},{"pid":"f74a232303e9d8dd1cc14a346835c94f19e100b7","tid":698276,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf8b380f588b507843a702597c43fcba64d4d01","tid":698276,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef2f492f3a01e771852dda544073290c1b892fc0","tid":698276,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T14:13:32.000Z","msg":"月亮同火星D金字塔係咪中國人過去起"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T01:19:30.000Z","msg":"月亮同火星嗰啲先係原裝外星人起<br />\n埃及嗰啲係古代中國人抄"},{"pid":"bbb944377059883346